Hello Dmitri,



It's not easy keeping up with themes across many property types and markets=
.  Following are some interesting highlights across several of the ~17 sect=
ors we cover. (Happy to offer a close look if interested).

(Note: Links to full reports only accessible to clients)



Industrial



Amazon....starting out as an online bookshop nearly three decades ago, Amaz=
on now accounts for an estimated ~40% of U.S. ecommerce market share and ~7=
% of all retail sales ex-auto and gas when including its third-party sales.=
 For most of the past fifteen years, Amazon's online sales growth has outpa=
ced overall U.S. ecommerce growth, though the trend has slightly reversed r=
ecently.



*         Industrial Insights - The Great Amazon Moderation: https://my.gre=
enstreet.com/research/reports/16513/download?region=3DNA&applyWaterMark=3D1

o   This report provides an in-depth analysis of Amazon's U.S. logistics ne=
twork at the national and market level.



