<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing">October 5, 2022</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing">Hello Dmitri,</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing">It&#8217;s not easy keeping up with themes across=
 many property types and markets.&nbsp; Following are some interesting
<b>highlights across several of the ~17 sectors</b> we cover. (Happy to off=
er a close look if interested).</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing"><i><span style=3D"font-size:9.0pt">(Note: Links t=
