<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing"><b><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.5pt">Industrial=
<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing"><span style=3D"font-size:11.5pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p=
></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing">Amazon&#8230;.starting out as an online bookshop =
nearly three decades ago, Amazon now accounts for an estimated ~40% of U.S.=
 ecommerce market share and ~7% of all retail sales ex-auto and gas when in=
cluding its third-party sales. For most
 of the past fifteen years, Amazon's online sales growth has outpaced overa=
ll U.S. ecommerce growth, though the trend has slightly reversed recently.<=
/p>
